<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시판 레이아웃</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

    <style>

        * {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
  padding: 20px;
}

.board-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 20px;
}

.board {
  background-color: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #dddddd;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.board h3 {
  color: red;
  font-size: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.board ul {
  list-style: none;
}

.board ul li {
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-size: 14px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;  /* 세로 정렬 */
}

.board ul li span {
  color: #888888;
  font-size: 12px;
  margin-top: 5px;  /* 제목과 시간 사이의 간격 */
}

    </style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="board-container">
    <div class="board">
        <h3>조회가 많은 게시글</h3>
        <ul>
            {{#Search}}
                <div class="board-item">
                    <p><strong>제목:</strong> <a href="/board/detail/{{id}}">{{title}}</a></p>
                    <li> <p><strong>작성자:</strong> {{nickname}}</p> </li>
                    <li> <p><strong>작성일자:</strong> {{createdAtFormat}}</p> </li>
                </div>
            {{/Search}}

            {{^Search}}
                <p>게시글이 없습니다.</p>
            {{/Search}}
        </ul>
    </div>

